data.text: @julianjon Well, I think I was having dietary issues AND someone shared a bug. So sick today! Everything from collarbones up hurts. Hoping I recover enough to get in a run tomorrow & stay on schedule + improve enough by Monday night to enjoy hubby's b-day dinner. 🤧
